data.description: A beautiful 4+ acre property situated just off SR 207 in East Palatka. Presently zoned Agricultural (AG) with a future land use designation of Commercial! This property offers 365ft of frontage on SR 207 and is partially cleared and fenced with a gorgeous live oak canopy and is currently used as a full-time residence. With the value of the property being in the land, the 2 story home is 2,000sf+ with 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths and being sod AS-IS. Located only minutes to downtown Palatka, shopping and 20 minutes from St. Augustine!
